{"type": "article", "id": 20689, "title": "冰箱贴", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-14T07:30:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143058fugC9ENz54SajpxV.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这组冰箱贴像一个小鸟的头，它用了橡木和磁铁两种材料。外圈的橡木有简单的缺口，弯曲出了小鸟的嘴，而磁铁是规整的圆形，放在靠近缺口的位置，是小鸟的眼睛，简单巧妙。它还可以吸上钢笔、钥匙等较大的物件，放在冰箱上增加了生活的趣味。有黑色、深棕色、浅棕色三种，售价 16.25 美元，<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/birp-magnet-for-fridge-or-whiteboard/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150538FKSwofBhv4OrcbNV.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"1410\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150539UeG6LpWJqiCxYatX.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"958\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.01914894\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150539wCgPUOJHG0pxySe3.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"912\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.97021277\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150540h7JjSeGAl15Nqibk.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"889\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.94574468\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}